img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8d680bd2d3d9ce57ef288e8c2b8f211ed82f73","tid":2188543,"uid":67340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:41:11.000Z","msg":"孫將軍再推"},{"pid":"a340204580209b1c3b11ab515d68c7d56fc1cc6e","tid":2188543,"uid":67340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:41:38.000Z","msg":"孫某老漢推"},{"pid":"c8e85027cb77dede1db02148f62b6f3b5997fbeb","tid":2188543,"uid":67340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c13ee30e25420ec024c307cc52083bbe0318a41","tid":2188543,"uid":67340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:59:32.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">睇新聞學英文</span></span>，嚟緊小弟都會<span class=\"gold\">每日早晚</span>簡單翻譯啲外國報導俾大家睇，等大家可以<span class=\"gold\">雙語</span>吸收資訊，學多啲英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />尤其係咁多位DSE仔女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家試緊啲排版，大家可以Comment下新排版會唔會清楚啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望睇完幫手Like+推，鍾意就Dog埋我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n--------------------------------------------------<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-54022461?intlink_from_url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world/asia/china&amp;link_location=live-reporting-story\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-54022461%3Fintlink_from_url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fchina%26link_location%3Dlive-reporting-story&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cbQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=22727cbe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-54022461%3Fintlink_from_url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fchina%26link_location%3Dlive-reporting-story&h=9d2a48d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-54022461?intlink_from_url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world/asia/china&amp;link_location=live-reporting-story</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">Hong Kong security law: UN experts voice deep concerns</span><br />\n<br />\n//The legislation has been <span class=\"red\">widely criticised </span>since it was imposed by Beijing in June after months of huge pro-democracy protests in Hong Kong last year. //<br />\n「上年連場大型民主抗爭後，北京喺六月立國安法，呢個立法一直俾<span class=\"red\">好多人圍屌</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//The law, which criminalises secession, subversion, and collusion with foreign forces, has <span class=\"red\">silenced</span> many protesters since it <span class=\"red\">came into effect</span>.//<br />\n「國安法規定分裂國家、顛覆國家同勾結外國勢力為非法行為，<span class=\"red\">實施後</span>令好多抗爭者<span class=\"red\">噤聲</span>。」<br />\n<span class=\"red\">Come into effect </span>解實施/推行，比起佢既同義詞感覺較informal (因人而異<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) 喺DSE寫關於policy既文，例如學校好唔好推行某項政策，呢隻字會幾好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，同義詞有 carry out, apply(小學雞), implement, enact, administer(官方的 提供), <span class=\"orange\">execute, enforce, impose</span> (強推), effectuate (又有執行，實現既意思)。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//On Friday the 14-page letter was posted on the UN human rights office website, 48 hours after it was sent to the Chinese government. //信Link: <a href=\"https://spcommreports.ohchr.org/TMResultsBase/DownLoadPublicCommunicationFile?gId=25487\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fspcommreports.ohchr.org%2FTMResultsBase%2FDownLoadPublicCommunicationFile%3FgId%3D25487&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cbQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=5d40a441\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://spcommreports.ohchr.org/TMResultsBase/DownLoadPublicCommunicationFile?gId=25487</a><br />\n「星期五(今日) ，呢封14頁既信喺寄俾中國政府既48小時後，上載於聯合國人權辦事處網頁。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//They said the new law's measures <span class=\"red\">do not conform to</span> China's legal obligations under international law. The experts also raised serious concerns about its impact on the freedoms that were guaranteed to Hong Kong when it was handed back to China from British control in 1997. They added that it <span class=\"red\">ran the &quot;grave risk&quot;</span> of targeting the legitimate activities of political opponents, critics, students, and lawyers among others. //<br />\n「專家話國安法嘅措施<span class=\"red\">並唔符合</span>中國喺國際法框架下嘅義務。佢地同時強烈關注國安法對1997年主權移交時所承諾嘅自由會有咩影響，補充指國安法瞄準政治對手、評論家、學生同埋律師其他人等等嘅合符情理嘅活動，<span class=\"red\">存在嚴重風險</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">Conform to</span> 解 遵守/符合一啲規則。呢個位我用「符合」係因為好譯啲。<br />\n<span class=\"red\">Run the risk of &hellip;</span> 解 冒著乜野風險, 小學雞啲可以用has/have the risk of &hellip;, 但如果你唔會特別形容係點樣既risk，直接作動詞寫 e.g. It risks the death of 300 civilians 都得<br />\n<span class=\"red\">Grave</span> 名詞解墓穴、墓碑，想像下嚴重到可以死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，Grave做形容詞解嚴重、重大既(負面)意思，個人覺得嚴重過serious，同義詞有 serious (中學牛)，<span class=\"orange\">acute, urgent</span>(迫切), <span class=\"orange\">pressing</span>(迫切), <span class=\"orange\">dire</span>(迫切), alarming(迫切到響警號<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//On Tuesday prominent activist Agnes Chow, who was among the group detained under the law last month, said <span class=\"red\">dissent in the city was being silenced</span>. //<br />\n//&quot;I hope the world, not only the whole of Hong Kong... could know that the national security law is actually not a legal thing, but <span class=\"red\">a political tool for the regime</span>, for the government to suppress political dissidents,&quot; AFP reported Ms Chow as saying.//<br />\n「星期二，出眾嘅抗爭者周庭BB<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上個月因國安法被拘留，指香港嘅<span class=\"red\">反對聲音正被滅聲</span>。「我希望全世界，唔止全香港&hellip;會明白國安法其實唔係法律上嘅野，而係<span class=\"red\">政權既政治工具</span>，用嚟打政治異見者。」AFP報導周庭BB<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />既說話。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//Beijing has said the legislation is needed to <span class=\"red\">tackle unrest and instability</span>.//<br />\n//It rejects criticism as <span class=\"red\">interference in its affairs.</span> //<br />\n「北京話國安法係用嚟<span class=\"red\">解決社會混亂同埋不穩</span>。佢唔同意<span class=\"red\">企图干预内政</span>的批评。」<br />\n(北京:專家食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n希望睇完幫手Like+推，鍾意就Dog埋我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n--------------------------------------------------<br />\n相關翻譯:<br />\n[進擊的王毅] Washington Post: 中國想喺歐洲亡羊補牢但食曬屎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2187932\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2187932</a><br />\n<br />\n(斷交部) 紐約時報: 美國進一步限制中國外交人員活動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gadEfS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gadEfS</a><br />\n<br />\n(第一年) BBC: 香港運動 - 5個引爆點<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fRMGzS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fRMGzS</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:42:18.000Z","msg":"孫立人五毛狗 拉"},{"pid":"456576a344749d4d2ceff5317f6971700e34cb7f","tid":2188543,"uid":67340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:42:42.000Z","msg":"我愛孫將軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"847d0e0a6903f87e86a0beabbc8455d3ffab1b70","tid":2188543,"uid":59363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:47:51.000Z","ms